data.description: Gorgeous 3 bed, 2 bath (Plus an Office) residence showcasing 2-car garage & RV gate in Rancho El Dorado is now on the market! Prepare to be impressed by a bright & airy interior offering spacious living areas w/wood-look floors, designer palette, & arched doorways. The immaculate kitchen offers new granite counter tops, backsplash, Kitchen recessed lighting and new appliances. Double doors open to the fabulous main bedroom with sitting area, a private bathroom with dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. You'll love hosting fun gatherings in the wonderful backyard with covered patio, built-in BBQ, a charming fireplace, sparkling blue pool, & a cozy firepit! You MUST see it!
